main.java.model.orderserver

Class OrderServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.model.orderserver.OrderServer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OrderServerRealExternal, OrderServerSimulatedInternal

    public abstract class OrderServer
extends java.lang.Object
    One OrderServer for one instrument type traded. OrderServer can be implemented as: OrderServerRealExternal - sends oreder to OutsideTradingSoftwareAPIConnection to be executed by the real market through a broker; or: OrderServerSimulatedInternal - this checks prices continuously to simulate fills internally Decision has to be made at start of trading and cannot be changed while program is running
